: "like sinking slowly to the ocean floor (utter boredom)"}, {"page": "87", "word": "inform on", "sentence": "She wouldn't [[inform on]] them, wouldn't report them to anyone.", "kor": "고자질하다/밀고하다", "eng": "to report someone's misdeeds"}, {"page": "87", "word": "authorities", "sentence": "She didn't tell the [[authorities]], the grown-ups in charge.", "kor": "당국/학교 관계자들", "eng": "the officials in charge"}, {"page": "87", "word": "unburdened herself", "sentence": "Aunt Alexandra [[unburdened herself]], pouring out all her complaints.", "kor": "털어놓다/짐을 덜다", "eng": "poured out her complaints"}, {"page": "87", "word": "gave me hell", "sentence": "She [[gave me hell]], scolding me up one side and down the other (idiom).", "kor": "혼내주다/호되게 야단치다", "eng": "scolded me severely (idiom)"}, {"page": "87", "word": "whichever struck his fancy", "sentence": "He'd do [[whichever struck his fancy]], whichever he happened to feel like.", "kor": "그의 기분에 따라/내키는 대로", "eng": "whichever he happened to feel like"}, {"page": "87", "word": "speak sharply to", "sentence": "She would [[speak sharply to]] us, in a cutting, scolding tone.", "kor": "날카롭게 말하다/톡 쏘아붙이다", "eng": "to speak in a sharp, cutting tone"}, {"page": "87", "word": "overalls", "sentence": "Scout wore [[overalls]], the loose one-piece work trousers.", "kor": "작업복/멜빵 바지", "eng": "loose one-piece work trousers"}, {"page": "87", "word": "fanatical", "sentence": "Aunt Alexandra was [[fanatical]] about it, fiercely, obsessively zealous.", "kor": "[fㅞ내티클] 광적인/극단적으로 열성적인", "eng": "obsessively zealous"}, {"page": "87", "word": "attire", "sentence": "She criticized my [[attire]], my clothing and dress.", "kor": "[어타이어] 복장/의복", "eng": "clothing; dress (formal)"}, {"page": "88", "word": "breeches", "sentence": "A girl should wear [[breeches]] only sometimes, the proper short riding trousers.", "kor": "승마용 바지/반바지", "eng": "riding trousers"}, {"page": "88", "word": "deportment", "sentence": "She lectured me on [[deportment]], on how a lady s