word": "House of Commons", "sentence": "He sat in the [[House of Commons]], the elected lower house of Parliament.", "kor": "하원 - 영국 의회", "eng": "the lower house of the British Parliament"}, {"page": "93", "word": "blew feathers in the air", "sentence": "He used to [[blew feathers in the air]], idly puffing them up to pass the time.", "kor": "공중에 깃털을 불다", "eng": "blew feathers into the air (an image of idleness)"}, {"page": "93", "word": "all about him men were losing their heads", "sentence": "[[All about him men were losing their heads]] — everyone around him panicking — while he stayed calm.", "kor": "그 주변의 모든 사람들이 정신을 잃고 있을 때", "eng": "while everyone around him panicked"}, {"page": "93", "word": "no sense whatsoever", "sentence": "It made [[no sense whatsoever]] to her, none at all.", "kor": "전혀 말이 안 되다", "eng": "makes no sense at all"}, {"page": "93", "word": "a lot to learn", "sentence": "She still had [[a lot to learn]], much yet to understand.", "kor": "배울 것이 많다", "eng": "much still to learn"}, {"page": "93", "word": "romped on", "sentence": "Uncle Jack had [[romped on]] her, scolded her fiercely (dialect).", "kor": "거칠게 다루다/혼내주다", "eng": "scolded fiercely (dialect)"}, {"page": "93", "word": "remorseful", "sentence": "He looked [[remorseful]], full of regret for it.", "kor": "후회스러운/뉘우치는", "eng": "full of regret"}, {"page": "93", "word": "on tenterhooks", "sentence": "She kept him [[on tenterhooks]], in anxious suspense (idiom).", "kor": "몹시 긴장하여/조마조마하여", "eng": "in anxious suspense (idiom)"}, {"page": "93", "word": "bathroom invective", "sentence": "She let loose some [[bathroom invective]], crude toilet-wall cursing.", "kor": "화장실 욕설/저속한 욕설", "eng": "crude toilet-wall swearing"}, {"page": "93", "word": "leaves nothing to the imagination", "sentence": "It [[leaves nothing to the imagination]], being utterly blunt and explicit (idiom).", "kor": "상상의 여지가 없다/매우 노골적이다", "eng": "is completely explicit (idiom)"}, {"page": "93", "word": "Lord Melbourne", "sentence"